name.k: ヒットマン スナイパー (Hitman Sniper)

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 極上のスナイパー体験

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: While Hitman GO carved out a bold new direction for Agent 47, his next iOS mission expertly captures the riveting gameplay of the venerable console series. You won’t be donning disguises to sneak into enemy compounds (the game’s all about sniping), but you still carefully scout each location, unravel the intricately woven level design, and then strike with impeccable timing—or die and try again. Hitman: Sniper does its legacy proud with 150 missions full of engrossing action and the series’ quirky sense of humor.
